	   <tr><td colspan=2>No.  All the Grifs in North Karanas drop identical feathers.  Griffons, Griffennes, or Griffawns.  Actually, never killed Grimfeather so I am not sure whether he drops any feather.<br>But all three of the other drop the same feather and they stack together.  To spawn fennes I would kill fawns, so I got quite a few feathers in my time.<br>Also, these sell to merchants for seven gold, but merchants sell them for seven plat.  So do an auction in North Karanas for a few plat if you're not going to hunt them.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
